/span><br />\n<br />\n　　雖然在競選過程中，有官方人員介入對手的一些選舉常見滋擾手段，如對睿內的跟蹤、電話暗示性地對兒子安全的威脅、對團隊相關成員的盯梢等，<span style=\"color: red;\">但最後還是讓「NO」營贏得勝選。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">宜家文宣策略除左要顯示政權黑暗（因為好多人已經麻木），<br />\n更應該帶出民主制度係未來嘅&quot;好&quot;，<br />\n為人民同抗爭者帶黎希望同動力，<br />\n咁先可以拉到藍絲同離地中產支持<br />\n<br />\n我地會贏，因為我地一定要贏<br />\n（多謝說書者推介）<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T07:51:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hkfactcheck.io/district/%E6%96%B0%E7%95%8C-%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E5%8D%80-%E5%A4%A9%E8%80%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkfactcheck.io%2Fdistrict%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2595%258C-%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E5%258D%2580-%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E8%2580%2580&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9gTszQqcSrFeuHGFn5Djw6E%3D&h=f46edabe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkfactcheck.io/district/%E6%96%B0%E7%95%8C-%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E5%8D%80-%E5%A4%A9%E8%80%80</a><br />\n智利依家進行嘅社運&uarr;都將近成功。"},{"pid":"6da1fdac5f81f65a6e5103efa91b5cb78eeda168","tid":1662115,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:02:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5c445c7a7cde33abac2111060c393915e118ac8","tid":1662115,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T00:45:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf157f23a34a397ef949a33e7f202475167b450b","tid":1662115,"uid":129848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T00:48:00.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"b5a31061c3fd058ac7e6299c3386b3a2541a9b13","tid":1662115,"uid":192848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T01:43:23.000Z","msg":"朝早推行動post"},{"pid":"511dfb91d63e8168962214aa7c2d38dd585b0f24","tid":1662115,"uid":299785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:09:27.000Z","msg":"Hope will conquer despair"},{"pid":"fd0803f365e7ad98174d648b7f96a443209dd16e","tid":1662115,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:02:23